  <summary date="2023-08-08T19:18:45Z" status="Introduced in House">Social Security 2100: A Sacred Trust

This bill makes changes to Social Security benefits, taxes, and other aspects of the program, including by raising the primary insurance amount, increasing the maximum taxable earnings that are subject to Social Security payroll taxes, and requiring Social Security account statements to be mailed unless the individual recipient opts for electronic delivery.</summary>
</bill>
